 Well, I had a good time, did several talks, and--get this! An
investigation. Or rather I kinda tagged along on a group&#39;s investigation and
used one of the boxes. There was entities answering questions, and
responding tot he group members. I gave the group the tape, so I won&#39;t be
able able to play those. On my own recordings, the spirits were pretty the
same as  get at home, and even my son come through wiht &quot;My father did
this&quot;, which I played for a larger group. I loaned a box to another group,
and they also got entities to answer questions, and interact. 

 RoboBox did perform for a group, with at least one meaningful comment. A
woman came to the table afte the talk, and asked &quot; Do they onokly talk for
you&quot;&quot;, and immediately RoboBox put out &quot;for you&quot;, followed after a few
seconds &quot;Loves to cook&quot;, the woman was a cook!

 The whole thing is very energy intense. 
